Assassin
Cost-Effective Materials;;1;Reduces the cost of Hungering Arrow by 30 Mana.
Siphoning Arrow;;1;50% of the damage dealt by Hungering Arrow is returned as Health to Valla.
Composite Arrows;;1;Increases the range of Multishot by 20%.
Rancor (Trait);;1;Each Hatred stack increases Attack Speed by 2%
Punishment (Trait);;1;Using an Ability grants 2 Hatred stacks.
Vampiric Assault;;4;Basic Attacks heal for 15% of the damage dealt.
Manticore;;4;Every 3rd Basic Attack against the same target deals 50% additonal damage.
Puncturing Arrow;;4;Hungering Arrow range increased by 25% and the number of times it can bounce to 3.
Arsenal;;4;Multishot also fires 3 grenades, which deal 35 damage.
Battle Momentum;;7;Basic Attacks reduce Ability cooldowns by 0.5 seconds.
Caltrops;;7;Drop 3 Caltrops while Vaulting. Caltrops do 25 damage and slow enemies by 20% for 2 seconds.
Repeating Arrow;;7;The cooldown for Hungering Arrow is reset when Vault is used.
Searing Attacks;;7;Activate to increase Basic Attack damage by 50% for 5 seconds. Each attack costs 15 Mana. 25s cooldown.
Strafe;;10;Rapidly attack nearby visible enemies for 30 damage per hit, prioritizing heroes over minions. Valla is able to move and use Vault while strafing. Lasts for 4 seconds. 50s cooldown.
Rain of Vengeance;;10;Launch 2 waves of Shadow Beasts that deal 100 damage to enemies within the target area, stunning for 0.5 seconds per wave.
Giant Killer;;13;Basic Attacks against enemy Heroes deal bonus damage equal to 1.5% of the Hero's max Health.
Frost Shot;;13;Multishot also slows by 40% for 2 seconds.
Pursuit (Trait);;13;When at 10 stacks of Hatred, the Movement Speed bonus increases to 20% total.
Tempered by Discipline (Trait);;13;Gain up to 10 stacks of Discipline after Hatred stacks are maxed. Basic Attacks heal for 3% of damage dealt per Discipline stack.
Spell Shield;;13;Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce all Ability Damage taken by 50% for 2 seconds. Can only trigger once every 30 seconds.
Executioner;;16;Basic Attacks deal 40% more damage against slowed, rooted, or stunned targets.
Tumble;;16;Vault gains an additional charge, allowing it to be cast twice in quick succession.
Blood for Blood;;16;Activate to steal 15% of target enemy's Max Health and slow its Movement Speed by 30% for 3 seconds. 60s cooldown.
Stoneskin;;16;Activate to gain 30% of your Max Health as Shields for 5 seconds.
Fury of the Storm;;20;Basic Attacks bounce twice to nearby enemies for 50% damage.
Bolt of the Storm;;20;Activate to teleport to a nearby location. 40s cooldown.
Vengeance;;20;Strafe also fires penetrating bolts in a line for 7.5 damage every 0.25 seconds.
Storm of Vengeance;;20;Increases the number of Shadow Beast waves to 4.